 be following up with the district councilor on the matter being discussed. I too will be following up on the issue. His suggestion of building an art museum so as to boost tourism is deemed necessary. Paul and I went to a museum the other day where we looked at all the big nineteenth-century oil paintings in the museum in minute detail in case we miss any wonderful things. He'll be throwing a party in a hotel instead of his place in case of disturbing his neighbours."},{"pid":"7933ea4861a4ad12c3a2decdb3082cd1347af3f3","tid":2057461,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"好靚呀<br />\n想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2e7a85262e7f06701f32bfa1752b37b2aa208a","tid":2057461,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7933ea4861a4ad12c3a2decdb3082cd1347af3f3","tid":2057461,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"好靚呀<br />\n想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"但係個湯好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986a806c35987c6bf477db1f25b96c4aba9b3d9a","tid":2057461,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"最鍾意食烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5f2c688548bf4743556cf87c5535fc629ad855","tid":2057461,"uid":313848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"邊隻烏冬好食"},{"pid":"9bf52a1a5d48e0bc41a67e10eea4da532c335d88","tid":2057461,"uid":106588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"咩湯"},{"pid":"54f51f79af05b44da42cd6e28ce70dbcd3cffe39","tid":2057461,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5f2c688548bf4743556cf87c5535fc629ad855","tid":2057461,"uid":313848,"like":0,"disl